    <string name="backup_info_title">How synchronization works</string>
    <string name="backup_info_desc">To keep multiple devices in sync, we recommend using \"Save to...\" and creating a file in the cloud (e.g., Google Drive). \n\n1. Press \"Save to...\" and create a file on your Google Drive.\n2. The app will now automatically save your progress there every time you win.\n3. On your other device, press \"Import file\" and select the SAME file. \n\nThe app will then automatically merge your best times from all devices into one shared overview, and use this file for future saves.</string>
